Install for TextMate
====================
- Create folder Erlang.tmbundle/Support/completion/
- Copy Makefile, support/, src/ and ebin/ into Erlang.tmbundle/Support/completion/
- Open Bundle Editor and add a command to the Erlang bundle:
  - call the command Completion
  - set Save to Nothing
  - copy/paste client.rb into the Command(s) box
  - set Input to Entire Document
  - set Output to Discard
  - set Key Equivalent to Alt-ESC (if you want it to be like other bundles)
  - set Scope Selector to source.erlang
